items.text: Fried spring roll is delicious. Special noodle soup is very tasty. Fried chicken wings is great too. Will be back for more.

The food here is so good that you need to queue up on most nights cos it's packed. Their spring rolls and chicken wings are really delicious.
Fried spring rolls, grilled pork vermicelli, fried quail and beef pho are all great in the taste department (prob not so in the nutrition one). Dried chilli paste is just lethal. U've been warned.
Most authentic Vietnamese restaurant i can find in Singapore :) damn good Pho , Cha Gio , Grilled Pork Cutlet with Rice and Ca Phe Sua Da :D reasonably priced too ;)
Always busy, sometimes a queue but quickly seated. Spring rolls, salad rolls, beef pho and grilled pork with rice noodles rock

Acceptable price, the service is so so. Everything is so so.
